@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Available Services";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/Customer/_Layout.cshtml";


}



<partial name="_CSS" />

<section class="hero pb-3 bg-cover bg-center d-flex align-items-center ml-1" style="background: url(/customer/img/ecommerce-2140603_1280.jpg)">
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="row px-4 px-lg-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<div class="container">
    <div class="card-detailes mt-5">
        <div class="card_img text-center">
            <i class="fas fa-shipping-fast"></i> <!-- Icon representing Shipping Services -->
        </div>
        <h3>Shipping Services</h3>
        <p>At InStock, we provide fast and reliable shipping services to ensure your products arrive on time. Whether you're ordering locally or internationally, we've got a range of options to meet your needs, including express delivery and eco-friendly choices.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-detailes mt-3">
        <div class="card_img text-center">
            <i class="fas fa-headset"></i> <!-- Icon representing Customer Support -->
        </div>
        <h3>Customer Support</h3>
        <p>Our customer support team is here to assist you with any inquiries, order updates, or issues you might encounter. Available through live chat, email, and phone, we're dedicated to ensuring your shopping experience is smooth and enjoyable.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-detailes mt-3">
        <div class="card_img text-center">
            <i class="fas fa-undo-alt"></i> <!-- Icon representing Return and Refund Policy -->
        </div>
        <h3>Return and Refund Policy</h3>
        <p>We stand behind the quality of our products and services. If you're not completely satisfied with your purchase, our return and refund policy makes it easy to return products and receive a refund or exchange. Visit our policy page for more details.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-detailes mt-3">
        <div class="card_img text-center">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> <!-- Icon representing Product Warranty -->
        </div>
        <h3>Product Warranty</h3>
        <p>Many of the products available at InStock come with a manufacturer's warranty for peace of mind. Additionally, we offer extended warranty services for select products, providing extra protection for your purchases.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-detailes mt-3">
        <div class="card_img text-center">
            <i class="fas fa-gift"></i> <!-- Icon representing Gift Services -->
        </div>
        <h3>Gift Services</h3>
        <p>Looking to send a gift? We offer gift wrapping services along with the ability to add a personal message to your order. Choose from our selection of wrapping options to make your gift extra special.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-detailes mt-3">
        <div class="card_img text-center">
            <i class="fas fa-user-friends"></i> <!-- Icon representing Membership and Rewards Program -->
        </div>
        <h3>Membership and Rewards Program</h3>
        <p>Join our Membership and Rewards Program to enjoy exclusive benefits, including discounts, early access to sales, and points on every purchase that can be redeemed for discounts on future orders. Sign up today and start saving!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-detailes mt-3">
        <div class="card_img text-center">
            <i class="fas fa-pen"></i> <!-- Icon representing Custom Orders -->
        </div>
        <h3>Custom Orders</h3>
        <p>For customers looking for something unique, we offer custom order services. Whether it's a personalized item or a product variant not typically stocked, our team will work with you to make your vision a reality.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-detailes mt-3">
        <div class="card_img text-center">
            <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> <!-- Icon representing Contact Information -->
        </div>
        <h3>Contact Information</h3>
        <p>For more information about our available services, please contact us at support@instock.com or visit our FAQ section. Our team is committed to providing you with the best service possible.</p>
    </div>
</div>

